    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            const ori_total = parseInt($('#section4').data('total'));
            let slider_loop = ori_total >= 3 ? true : false;
            $('#section4').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: slider_loop,
                dummySlide: slider_loop,
				afterSlide: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
					if(slider_loop) {
						if(current_page == ori_total) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2).Slider('start');
						}
						if(current_page == ori_total * 2 + 1) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1).Slider('start');
						}
					}
				},
                afterInit: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
                    if(slider_loop) {
                        slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2);
                    }
                    else {
                        slider.Slider('jump', total_page);
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section5" data-total="6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg bg-colour3"></div>
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Life at IS</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="record-slider">
            <div class="slider-container">
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/c29ffb6f990f6e7b1c1ab98d19667007.jpg" alt="IMG_3718-1" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>SPORTS</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We inspire your child to lead active, healthy lives through our inclusive sports program and community celebrations.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/3c2450015481d71e225cd538d3cf27e3.jpg" alt="IMG_0936-1" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>ACTIVITIES</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We wholeheartedly embrace creativity, providing your child abundant opportunities to explore the performing, visual, and creative arts.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/270ff0971c9a2b66152c2ddb6e5dbc6d.jpg" alt="IMG_5113edit" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>INTERHOUSE</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We welcome your child into one of our six Houses, fostering friendships and engaging in diverse activities.
that promote a sense of belonging and ownership.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/our_houses/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/504ed84ccb5cae2d7e6d4889869fecfa.png" alt="Untitled design (5)" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>STUDENT LEADERSHIP</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We encourage your child to pursue their passions and drive change through student-led activities and initiatives, helping them build essential soft skills as leaders and make a meaningful impact in their areas of interest.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/student_leadership/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/d6770bd1966c419d57c96850f21fbca1.png" alt="Untitled design (6)" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>QUEST WEEK</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Quest Week takes learning outside of the walls of the classroom. Students are encouraged to make connections and build relationships, whilst also being pushed outside of their comfort zones.
Our aim is to inspire students to become global citizens who nurture respectful relationships, are curious about the world around them, and are committed to making lasting change.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/0e333b3159ee543ea7d9b32dca6cf5b3.jpg" alt="IMG_8489-1" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>COMMUNITY ENGAGEMENT</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>At Island School, we foster your child's community spirit and responsibility through required coursework and impactful community projects.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://island.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/community_service/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/c29ffb6f990f6e7b1c1ab98d19667007.jpg" alt="IMG_3718-1" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>SPORTS</span>
                            </h3>
