                        <img src="/cache/img/cea3f1386af2ef9d4d1e41b9119fc14d.jpg" alt="601776471_18436278583105991_5899271246645852885_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="98">
                        <time>17/12/2025</time>
                        <h3>This year's Christmas celebrations at Island School were a delightful festive occasion, held from December 9-12! The holiday spirit was alive, with Christmas music playing and karaoke during breaks. Activities included the PTA Plush Sale, Elements Marketplace, Christmas cookie decoration, and the Senior Phase Christmas Quiz, where Fleming house emerged as the winner.<br>Funds raised from all the events will go toward supporting the Tai Po Relief Fund.</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/9228718c152cb0fb4f4999f5784e3acc.jpg" alt="601438282_18436278121105991_8616789884568789357_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                    </div>
        <div class="btns">
