                    <time>06/02/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>After months of hard work, Harry Potter and the Cursed Child enchanted the stage at Borrett Theatre with four magical performances from February 3 to 5. Our talented students brought this beloved story to life, supported by an amazing production team.<br><br>A heartfelt thank you to everyone who attended and to Mr. McCracken, Ms. Kawano and Mrs. Lacey Vittachi for their incredible leadership and creativity, along with our dedicated technicians.<br><br>We look forward to more exciting events after the Lunar New Year Break, including our Spring Concert and IB Visual Arts Exhibition!</h3>
