                    <time>23/01/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>On January 20th, we were thrilled to celebrate the resounding success of the Year 11 Social Action Exhibition. Since the start of this academic year, students have been immersed in group social action projects as part of their Global Perspectives IGCSE. This initiative, held under our Explorations programme, focuses on developing core competencies essential to future success in higher education and the modern workforce. By tackling key global issues firsthand, our students are truly evolving into informed global citizens.</h3>
